    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a medium sized pot (with a matching lid) over a medium heat with a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s]</strong> in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced leek</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the leek is beginning to soften</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>drained cannellini beans</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and your <strong>dried oregano</strong> to the pot with the leek and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> with 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[675ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[900ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pot and bring to a boil over a high heat</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, add your <strong>tomato & mozzarella tortelloni </strong>to the pot and cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until the tortellini is cooked with a slight bite \u2013 this is your <strong>veg-packed minestrone soup with tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/veg-packed-minestrone-soup-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>veg-packed minestrone soup with tomato & mozzarella tortelloni </strong>in a bowl topped with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Garnish with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
